org.eclipselabs.mongoemf

Interface DBObjectBuilderFactory


  • public interface DBObjectBuilderFactory
    This interface provides the API for for the DBObjectBuilder factory. If you wish to use a custom DBObjectBuilder, you must create a factory class for your builder that implements this interface.
    Author:
    bhunt
